  fhir:text [
     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xml:lang=\"en\" lang=\"en\"><hr/><p><b>English</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CapabilityStatement AsServerDPCapabilityStatement</b></p><a name=\"en-AsServerDPCapabilityStatement\"> </a><a name=\"en-hcAsServerDPCapabilityStatement\"> </a><h2 id=\"en-title\"/><ul><li>Implementation Guide Version: 1.2.0-snapshot-2 </li><li>FHIR Version: 4.0.1 </li><li>Supported Formats: <code>json</code></li><li>Published on: 2025-08-11 13:49:59+0000 </li><li>Published by: Agence du Numérique en Santé (ANS) - 2-10 Rue d'Oradour-sur-Glane, 75015 Paris </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Note to Implementers: FHIR Capabilities</strong></p><p>Any FHIR capability may be 'allowed' by the system unless explicitly marked as 'SHALL NOT'. A few items are marked as MAY in the Implementation Guide to highlight their potential relevance to the use case.</p></blockquote><h2 id=\"en-rest\">FHIR RESTful Capabilities</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"en-mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"/></div><h3 id=\"en-resourcesCap1\">Capabilities by Resource/Profile</h3><h4 id=\"en-resourcesSummary1\">Summary</h4><p>The summary table lists the resources that are part of this configuration, and for each resource it lists:</p><ul><li>The relevant profiles (if any)</li><li>The interactions supported by each resource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>ype are only present if at least one of the resources has support for them.</li><li><span>The required, recommended, and some optional search parameters (if any). </span></li><li>The linked resources enabled for <code>_include</code></li><li>The other resources enabled for <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>The operations on the resource (if any)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">C</b></th><th><b title=\"Required and recommended search parameters\">Searches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Organization1-1\">Organization</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-organization.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-organization|1.2.0-snapshot-2</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>_id, _lastUpdated, active, address, address-city, address-line, address-postalcode, data-information-system, data-registration-authority, identifier, identifier-type, mailbox-mss, name, partof, pharmacy-licence, type</td><td><code>*</code>, <code>Organization:partof</code></td><td><code>Device:organization</code>, <code>HealthcareService:organization</code>, <code>PractitionerRole:organization</code></td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Device1-2\">Device</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-device.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-device|1.2.0-snapshot-2</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>_id, _lastUpdated, data-information-system, data-registration-authority, identifier, manufacturer, model, organization, status, type</td><td><code>*</code>, <code>Device:organization</code></td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-Practitioner1-3\">Practitioner</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-practitioner.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-practitioner|1.2.0-snapshot-2</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>_id, _lastUpdated, active, data-information-system, data-registration-authority, family, given, identifier, identifier-type, mailbox-mss, name, number-smartcard, qualification-code, type-smartcard</td><td/><td><code>PractitionerRole:practitioner</code></td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-PractitionerRole1-4\">PractitionerRole</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-practitionerrole.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-practitionerrole|1.2.0-snapshot-2</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>_id, _lastUpdated, active, data-information-system, data-registration-authority, identifier, mailbox-mss, organization, practitioner, role</td><td><code>*</code>, <code>PractitionerRole:organization</code>, <code>PractitionerRole:practitioner</code></td><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#en-HealthcareService1-5\">HealthcareService</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-healthcareservice-healthcare-activity.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/annuaire/StructureDefinition/as-dp-healthcareservice-healthcare-activity|1.2.0-snapshot-2</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>_id, _lastUpdated, _profile, active, characteristic, data-information-system, data-registration-authority, identifier, organization, service-category, service-type</td><td><code>*</code>, <code>HealthcareService:organization</code></td><td/><td/></tr></tbody></table></div><hr/><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"en-Organization1-1\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Organization</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-organization.html\">AS Donnée Publique Organization Profileversion: 1.2.0-snapshot-2)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_id</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'ID de la ressource Organization.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_lastUpdated</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Renvoie uniquement les ressources dont la dernière mise à jour correspond à la période spécifiée. Les préfixes supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont gt, ge et eq.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">active</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche que les ressources Organizations actives.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">address</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'adresse de la structure.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">address-city</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur la commune de la structure.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-address-line.html\">address-line</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'adresse.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">address-postalcode</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le code postal de la structure.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-information-system.html\">data-information-system</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le système d'information.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-registration-authority.html\">data-registration-authority</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'autorité d'enregistrement.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur tous les identifiants de structures.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>identifier-type</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le type d'identifiant. Ce paramètre de recherche est voué à être remplacé par le modifier :of-type du paramètre de recherche identifier.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-mailbox-mss.html\">mailbox-mss</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur les Messageries Sécurisées de Santé (MSS) rattachées aux structures.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/organization.html#search\">name</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur la raison sociale des structures. Les modifiers supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont contains, exact et text.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>partof</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur tous les établissements géographiques rattachés à une même entité juridique.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-pharmacy-licence.html\">pharmacy-licence</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le numéro de licence des pharmacies officines.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>type</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le type de structure (entité juridique, entité géographique), le secteur d'activité, la catégorie d'établissement, le code APE/NAF, le statut juridique de la structure, les modalités de participation au service hospitalier et le type d'établissement (principal ou secondaire).</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"en-Device1-2\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Device</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-device.html\">AS Donnée Publique Device Profileversion: 1.2.0-snapshot-2)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_id</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'ID de la ressource Device.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_lastUpdated</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Renvoie uniquement les ressources dont la dernière mise à jour correspond à la période spécifiée. Les préfixes supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont gt, ge et eq.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-information-system.html\">data-information-system</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le système d'information.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-registration-authority.html\">data-registration-authority</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'autorité d'enregistrement.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'ID de la ressource Device.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">manufacturer</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur la marque des équipements matériels lourds.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">model</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le modèle des équipements matériels lourds.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">organization</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur tous les Devices liés à l'Organization indiquée.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">status</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>active | inactive | entered-in-error | unknown.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/device.html#search\">type</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le type de l'équipement matériel lourd.</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"en-Practitioner1-3\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Practitioner</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-practitioner.html\">AS Donnée Publique Practitioner Profileversion: 1.2.0-snapshot-2)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_id</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'ID de la ressource Practitioner.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_lastUpdated</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Renvoie uniquement les ressources dont la dernière mise à jour correspond à la période spécifiée. Les préfixes supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont gt, ge et eq.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">active</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche que les ressources Practitioners actives.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-information-system.html\">data-information-system</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le système d'information.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-registration-authority.html\">data-registration-authority</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'autorité d'enregistrement.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">family</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le nom d'exercice des Professionnels intervenant dans le système de Santé. Les modifiers supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont contains, exact et text.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">given</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le prénom d'exercice des Professionnels intervenant dans le système de Santé. Les modifiers supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont contains, exact et text.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur tous les identifiants des activités intervenant dans le système de Santé.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>identifier-type</td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le type d'identifiant (Identifiant National des Professionnels intervenant dans le système de Santé (INPS), RPPS, ADELI, etc.). Ce paramètre de recherche est voué à être remplacé par le modifier :of-type du paramètre de recherche identifier.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-mailbox-mss.html\">mailbox-mss</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur les Messageries Sécurisées de Santé (MSS) rattachées aux Professionnels. Les modifiers supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont contains et exact.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitioner.html#search\">name</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Une recherche définie par le serveur qui peut correspondre à n'importe quel champ de HumanName. Ici, le préfixe correspond à la civilité des professionnels intervenant dans le système de santé. Les modifiers supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont contains, exact et text.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-number-smartcard.html\">number-smartcard</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le numéro de carte des Professionnels.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-qualification-code.html\">qualification-code</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le diplôme, l'exercice professionnel et le savoir-faire.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-type-smartcard.html\">type-smartcard</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur le type de carte des Professionnels.</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"en-PractitionerRole1-4\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>PractitionerRole</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-as-dp-practitionerrole.html\">AS Donnée Publique PractitionerRole Profileversion: 1.2.0-snapshot-2)</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>search-type</code>, <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_id</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'ID de la ressource PractitionerRole.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/resource.html#search\">_lastUpdated</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Renvoie uniquement les ressources dont la dernière mise à jour correspond à la période spécifiée. Les préfixes supportés par ce paramètre de recherche sont gt, ge et eq.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/practitionerrole.html#search\">active</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche que les ressources PractitionerRole actives.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-as-sp-data-information-system.html\">data-information-system</a></td><td><code>token</code></